Carstens Says Greek Restructuring Not a Solution, Europa Reports

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-05-30T16:40:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/carstens-says-greek-restructuring-not-a-solution-europa-reports.html
Bank of Mexico Governor Agustin
Carstens said restructuring Greek debt will not provide a
solution to the country’s economic problems, Europa Press
reported, citing comments he made at an event in  Madrid  today.  Such a step may provide a temporary boost to the country’s
economy while adding to its problems in the long run, the agency
cited Carstens as saying.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
